# Install sdk
$ sudo android

# Get errors
$ sudo android update sdk -u 

# Create
$ android create project --target 1 --name HelloAndroid --path ./HelloAndroidAppProject --activity HelloAndroidAppActivity --package com.example.helloandroid

$ android list avd

## Make
$ ant debug
$ ant release

## Install
$ emulator -avd avd-name
$ adb install bin/HelloAndroid-debug.apk

